Washoku Zen Selection*
Our Washoku Zen selection is a collection of artfully
prepared Japanese dishes served in two courses:
COURSE ONE
Start with bite-sized portions of salmon sushi with
fish eggs, roasted lime-flavored beef with miso,
quick-blanched tuna, broiled salmon, sansho-
lavoree sweel smer seaweeo-avoreo tounoen
and somen noodles topped with egg.
COURSE TWO
Continue with braised pork kakuni with sautéed
orons, wille reek unenne, oreen oean and carrot
flower, steamed rice and Japanese-pickled
vegetables to finish this bento box-style meal.
Accompanied by soothing green tea.
